Game Core assignment for 4160
Enes Cakir

Makefile commands are
    make
    make clean

Command to run the game
     ./myGame
   
  
     
A tile map is used as the background for the game, and each image is scaled to 32 by 32. 

Game is the class used for the game's engine
GameObject is the class for the player object
TextureManager is the class used to render images into textures
Map is the class used to create a tile map background

Two methods for movement in Game
    1. The directional keys
        Up
        Down
        Left
        Right
    2. W A S D
        W is Up
        A is Left
        S is Down
        D is Right

Game will not allow movement outside of the window


